# Implementation Plan - Responsive Layout & Automated Sidebar

The goal is to make the LMS application fully responsive across all devices and zoom levels. This includes an automated sidebar that transitions between expanded, mini (icons only), and hidden (mobile drawer) states based on the screen width.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The sidebar will now automatically collapse to icons-only mode on medium screens (768px - 1024px) and hide completely behind a hamburger menu on small screens (< 768px). 
> The main content area will dynamically adjust its margin to prevent overlapping.

